Dragon Priest Profiles & Motivations
Ultimate Goal: The Apotheosis Ritual
The Dragon Priests don't just serve Alduin. Centuries of undeath twisted their ambition. They will use Alduin to bring world to brink, then hijack his power at Bromjunaar Sanctuary using collected masks. Konahrik's mask is the vessel for the new god they'll collectively create.
