Nahkriin the Guardian
Role: Spymaster, Information Warfare
Tomb: Skuldafn (guards portal to Sovngarde)
Primary Duty: Serve Alduin directly
Strategy: Sow distrust and paranoia, prevent unified resistance
Methods: Silent sabotage, false flag operations, intelligence gathering
Vokun the Shadow
Role: Master Tactician, Military Commander
Tomb: High Gate Ruins
Strategy: Seize strategic military assets, establish forward operating bases
Methods: Night raids, psychological torture via Illusion magic, spectral interrogators
Personality: Cold, calculating, views war as chess
