Role: Weapon of Vengeance
Tomb: Forelhost (site of his historical defeat)
Strategy: Not conquest but revengeΓÇömake descendants suffer
Methods: Environmental warfare, alchemical plagues, scorched earth
Personality: Fury incarnate, surrounded by ghosts of defeat
Otar the Mad
Role: The Tyrant King
Tomb: Ragnvald
Strategy: PoliticalΓÇödoesn't see changed world, sees HIS kingdom temporarily occupied
Methods: Declarations, tribute demands, enforcement of "ancient law"
Personality: Delusional royalty, views Jarls as rebellious subjects
Morokei the Glorious
Role: Archmage, Ritual Master
Tomb: Labyrinthian
Strategy: The true endgameΓÇöApotheosis Ritual
