Notes on Pacing
This clock assumes a 45-session campaign with the following Act structure:
Act I (Pre-Session 1): Sandbox adventures, "normal" Skyrim
Act II (Sessions 1-16): Party chartered as Wardens, Torygg's assassination, navigating political chaos
Act III (Sessions 17-32): Seeking Greybeards, Elder Scroll quest, darkest hour
Act IV (Sessions 33-45): Final choice between Aedric/Daedric paths, confronting both Alduin and Dragon Cult
The clock can be adjusted for shorter/longer campaigns by modifying session counts per phase while maintaining the same Tier progression and narrative beats.


